M|rules|title: Cache Property Access in Loops
M|rules|impact: LOW-MEDIUM
M|rules|impactDescription: reduces lookups
M|rules|tags: javascript, loops, optimization, caching
M|rules|Cache object property lookups in hot paths.
M|rules|**Incorrect (3 lookups × N iterations):**
M|rules|```typescript
M|rules|for (let i = 0; i < arr.length; i++) {
M|rules|process(obj.config.settings.value)
M|rules|}
M|rules|```
M|rules|**Correct (1 lookup total):**
M|rules|```typescript
M|rules|const value = obj.config.settings.value
M|rules|const len = arr.length
M|rules|for (let i = 0; i < len; i++) {
M|rules|process(value)
M|rules|}
M|rules|```